# Plugin Hub package excludes (path-prefix match, relative to plugin folder).
#
# web/data ships a small bundled SAMPLE city (planx_manifest.json + yerlesim/*.geojson)
# so the viewer is never empty on first open. When the user runs the plugin, the
# real OSM export overwrites it. Only the heavy/runtime-only DEM raster is excluded.
web/data/dem
docs
.github
__pycache__
*.pyc
